<p>I'm Dr. Gears. I used to write a great deal, but have been off the map for&#8230;quite a while, really.</p>
<p>However, I did rather well when i was more active, and still pop up with the odd story now and then. I still love this place, and every madman (madwoman? madbeing?) here, and it seems it's generally reciprocated. I am, as always, trying to produce new content, but with such a deep talent pool these days&#8230;I'm getting off track.</p>
<p>I've been active with the community since before there really was one, back in the /x/ days. I figure people might like to poke me about things, ask questions or what have you, so here I am.</p>
<p>Just trying to say hello, get back into the swing of things. Fire away.</p>

