<p>That's the nutty bit, it's rare I get deeply unsettled by things. Maybe I'm jaded, maybe I just get too in to the story, but things typically hit me well after my initial exposure.</p>
<p>It sounds dumb, but 173 probably elicited the worst reaction. This was back when /x/ was new, and 173 was just a random creepypasta floating around. The Holders series was the big creepypasta series at the time&#8230;anyway, I clicked on the picture, looked, closed it, and went and did other things for a bit. It was so damn WEIRD. Days later, I mustered up the will to actually read the entry, got interested in it, and now I'm here.</p>
<p>I think that was about the strongest reaction I've had. That's not to say I've not lost sleep or needed a hug now and then, but that's the time that sticks out the most.</p>

